{"tid":741086,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"數學題一問！","createTime":"2018-07-13T11:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T13:51:16.000Z","uid":186524,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa2058b883452d4ae9efa84edfa7f48d0e99bad","tid":741086,"uid":186524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"一個水塔用c水閘，可以用11分鐘將水排走哂，而如果用d水閘就要用18分鐘先可以將水排走哂。如果同時開哂c同d閘要用幾耐時間先可以將啲水排哂？<br />\n求咁多位大神教教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192fa7718d871f4fb8e79edb7b0803e8eaa8e52b","tid":741086,"uid":39894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"1/(1/11+1/18)<br />\n<br />\n轉返速率就計到 <br />\n好似中四學"},{"pid":"e4ee9ddd70aa773ce9801b483c8a515dabf06d63","tid":741086,"uid":79161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"1/(1/11+1/18)"},{"pid":"3797f1a4ad8e59aea099a9c815c6fb9c3471cd0b","tid":741086,"uid":116511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"假設水池有198公升水<br />\n<br />\nC閘可以每分鐘排18公升水 用11分鐘清空水池<br />\n<br />\nD閘可以每分鐘排11公升水 用18分鐘清空水池<br />\n<br />\nC閘加D閘每分鐘排11+18=29公升水<br />\n用嘅時間就係198/29 =6.83分鐘"},{"pid":"90b3adae7c7e4ee48ae86e5afabbdce134fc11f1","tid":741086,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:38:20.000Z","msg":"假設水閘的水總容量為V, (unit = m^3)<br />\n       水閘C排水的速度為c, (unit = m^3/min)<br />\n        水閘D排水的速度為d, (unit = m^3/min)<br />\n        (假設排水的速度不變)<br />\n<br />\n水閘C用11分鐘排水-&gt;V=11c<br />\n水閘D用18分鐘排水-&gt;V=18d<br />\n<br />\n現在水閘C和D一齊開,假設排水時間為t, (unit = min)<br />\nct + dt = V<br />\n(V/11)t + (V/18)t = V<br />\nt = 1/(1/11+1/18)"},{"pid":"7d1579812864ab82d5b3c2a112b9985737330497","tid":741086,"uid":116511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3797f1a4ad8e59aea099a9c815c6fb9c3471cd0b","tid":741086,"uid":116511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc